Package: typMisc
Title: Miscellaneous R functions for typst.
Version: 0.1.0
URL: https://freierson.github.io/typstable/, https://github.com/freierson/typstable
BugReports: ggrothendieck@gmail.com
Authors@R:
    person("G.", "Grothendieck", email = "ggrothendieck@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A small collection of helper functions and S3 methods designed to
  streamline the generation of Typst code within Quarto documents. Includes
  tools for handling raw Typst blocks, managing table notes, and controlling
  document layout properties like figure breakability.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
